quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,aur yeh duniya ki zindagi to sirf khail aur tamasha hai aur ( hamesha ki ) zindagi ( ka maqam ) to akhirat ka ghar hai. kash yeh ( log ) samajte
  29,65,phir jab yeh kashti mein sawaar hotay hain to khuda ko pkarte ( aur ) khalis usi ki ibadat karte hain. lekin jab woh unn ko nijaat day kar khushki par pouncha deta hai to jhat shirk karne lagey jatay hain
  29,66,taakay jo hum ne unn ko bakhsha hai uss ki nashukri karen aur faida athayin ( so kher ) anqareeb unn ko maloom hojaye ga
  29,67,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne haram ko maqam aman banaya hai aur log is ke gird vnwah se uchak liye jatay hain.kiya yeh log baatil par aitqaad rakhtay hain aur khuda ki nematon ki nashukri karte hain
  29,68,aur is se zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhay ya jab haq baat uss ke paas aeye to is ki takzieeb kere.kiya kafiroon ka thikana jahannum mein nahi hai ?
  29,69,aur jin logon ne hamaray liye koshish ki hum unn ko zaroor apne raste dikha den ge. aur khuda to naiko karon ke sath hai
  30,1,Alif Laaam Meeem
  30,2,( ehley ) room maghloob hogaye
  30,3,nazdeek ke malik mein aur woh maghloob honay ke baad anqareeb ghalib ajayeen ge
  30,4,chand hi saal mein pehlay bhi aur peechay bhi khuda hi ka hukum hai aur uss roz momin khush ho jaien ge
  30,5,( yani ) khuda ki madad se. woh jisay chahta hai madad deta hai aur woh ghalib ( aur ) meharban hai
